{"tid":2084042,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[行動post] 唔洗再問71出定唔出，而係出到去做乜","createTime":"2020-06-29T06:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T15:15:05.000Z","uid":32355,"like":119,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"2e88c492161808ece9a1234a2b34553f2f338aa0","tid":2084042,"uid":32355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"民陣仲上訴緊<br />\n遊行詳情細節都仲未知<br />\n但今日已經629<br />\n而家唔傾定根本唔夠時間宣傳出去<br />\n<br />\n（同埋肯定上訴失敗<br />\n之後民陣應該唔會再講太多<br />\n靠就靠我地自己）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喱個post係想大家就唔同細節投票<br />\n大方向係由銅鑼灣行去金鐘<br />\n但：<br />\n<br />\n1. 彩虹戰衣vs black block<br />\n按彌敦道嘅經驗<br />\n基本上着咩衫都一定鳩拉<br />\n但彩虹戰衣好處係易聚人<br />\n尤其後生以外「進入」sogo一帶係毫無難度<br />\n一旦拉埋堆藍屍中產就一舉兩得<br />\n<br />\n壞處就係畫面唔靚<br />\n而且分唔到自己人<br />\n不過按住人流咁行其實大家都知咩事<br />\n畢竟今次都係行俾美國睇<br />\n夠人數逼爆銅鑼灣再放上twitter其實都夠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n彩虹戰衣-正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全黑-----負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9baabbc9599417b6c6fd4cbd92f188a038d2524","tid":2084042,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"堆"},{"pid":"5980ea8a34ef1dfbda72cdea0e6e6d99ab6d57d4","tid":2084042,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1b24ced81042dfec64f64ef821fde75df12857","tid":2084042,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:15:22.000Z","msg":"帶旗一齊fing<br />\n利申：畫面撚"},{"pid":"99ac0953b6e5346ee04a2a4a2a59d6562db32268","tid":2084042,"uid":32355,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"2. 靜默遊行vs舉野叫口號<br />\n前者相對安全<br />\n但連算唔算遊行都成問題<br />\n不過靜默遊行都唔係第一次<br />\n如果71個重點係逼爆港島<br />\n咁其實有足夠價值去咁做<br />\n<br />\n唔嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da464a8da0fcd73196793bc7c0455b4ac2ef411","tid":2084042,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fd47e02f5c539a7563b1c682ff0cbf936c36d7","tid":2084042,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"推行動po"},{"pid":"9720430ab7bc46c1091a289f2bd462f27e2ad419","tid":2084042,"uid":32355,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"3. 佔路vs行行人路<br />\n其實喱點有少少多餘<br />\n因為人一多其實點都佔啲<br />\n爭在係「主動佔路」定「盡量行行人路」<br />\n<br />\n不過啲狗對住路人都可以賞花杏仁露<br />\n個人認為完全守法都冇太大意思<br />\n<br />\n行出馬路-正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行行人路-負評"},{"pid":"ebc74e71047bb5e6ec7dea32bc0d0bb64e27f8ef","tid":2084042,"uid":32355,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:34:44.000Z","msg":"4. 老幼出唔出席<br />\n講真年年71都係多主題嘅總結遊行<br />\n由特首落台，到環保/平權/動保都有人講<br />\n所以年年係聚晒唔同光譜同年紀<br />\n先至一直都咁多人<br />\n<br />\n所以預埋佢地嘅話<br />\n所有屌狗/引狗放tg嘅行為全部唔做得<br />\n連裝都唔可以着上身<br />\n（甚至文宣圖都拎啲和平啲嘅）<br />\n<br />\n冚家都出動--------正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高風險留俾我地啦-負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68a29eed726344b856044e6471978f9f9e9d243","tid":2084042,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"啱啱仲見到有手足喺tg吹雞<br />\n話中山公園起步中聯辦終點<br />\n<br />\n開放討論啦"},{"pid":"612eb8db3c75ff9d19b6d65dd83f179403717fa1","tid":2084042,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1b24ced81042dfec64f64ef821fde75df12857","tid":2084042,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc